% Facts: Associating fruits with their colors
fruit_color(apple, red).
fruit_color(banana, yellow).
fruit_color(grapes, purple).
fruit_color(orange, orange).
fruit_color(kiwi, green).
fruit_color(lemon, yellow).
fruit_color(strawberry, red).
fruit_color(mango, yellow).

% Rule: Find the color of a fruit
find_color(Fruit, Color) :- fruit_color(Fruit, Color).

% Rule: Find fruits of a specific color
find_fruit_by_color(Color, Fruit) :- fruit_color(Fruit, Color).
